# Set the default behavior, in case people don't have core.autocrlf set.
# （核心！仓库统一存 LF，即使你在 Windows 用 CRLF 编辑也没问题）
* text=auto

# Explicitly declare text files you want to always be normalized
# （可选：明确声明源码文件，让 Git 更严格规范化）
*.c text
*.h text
*.cpp text
*.java text
*.py text
*.js text
*.ts text
*.jsx text
*.tsx text
*.html text
*.css text
*.md text
*.json text
*.yml text
*.yaml text

# Force LF for shell scripts and Unix-style files（强烈推荐！）
# （这些文件在 Windows 检出也强制用 LF，避免脚本在 Linux/Mac 上出问题）
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf
*.zsh text eol=lf
Makefile text eol=lf

# Declare files that will always have CRLF on checkout（很少用，仅 Windows 项目需要）
# *.sln text eol=crlf   # 如果你有 Visual Studio 项目才取消注释

# Denote all files that are truly binary and should not be modified.
# （防止图片、字体等被 Git 错误当成文本而损坏）
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary